  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Benjamin Kawer.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Last name is spelled K-A-W-E-R.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My first name has never been changed, and it's B-E-N-J-A-M-I-N.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In any language it was the same spelling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was my name at birth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, with the exception that during the war I was called-- when I arrived in Belgium I was called Beno-- B-E-N-O, strictly an abbreviation for Ben in Belgium and--",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "May 25, 1925.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm 71.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in Ostroleka, spelled O-S-T-R-O-L-E-N-K-A.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was Poland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, our family consisted of-- I had two sisters and one brother, father and mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the youngest one of four children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I left-- my parents left the city where I was born when I was two years old, which makes it approximately 1927.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They moved to another city called Hajnowka, which was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was about 180 kilometers away from the first city where I was born.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is where my parents made their home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They have moved there simply because my grandfather, my father's father, moved there about a couple of years before that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I guess the opportunities were there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My grandfather moved there also simply because his father, who was a very wealthy man before the Russian Revolution-- of course, he has lost everything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he told his son, which is my grandfather, Moshe, we are moving to the new frontiers-- this is after Poland has gained their independence in about 1918-- because there are better opportunities there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this is where my-- this is when my grandfather left in about 19-- probably-- 26 or so or '25, and my father followed-- my father and his brother, both of them.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were two unmarried daughters, the girls-- I mean, my-- my grandfather's children, who also moved to the same city.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
